     C                     Z-ADD-8        PA
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@ODAT
     C                     Z-ADD0         P@OTIM
      *
     C                     CALL 'DATR49'
     C                     PARM           P@IDAT  80
     C                     PARM           P@ITIM  60
     C                     PARM           PF      1
     C                     PARM           PA      50
     C                     PARM           P@ODAT  80
